1
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:32,400
Restore perfusion.

2
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:33,120
Copy.

3
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:35,840
Cerebral oxygen 62.

4
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:37,120
BP 30 over 20.

5
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:41,040
Prepare to rewarm.

6
00:00:41,800 --> 00:00:42,400
Start rewarming.

7
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:47,200
The vessels are too poor.

8
00:00:49,080 --> 00:00:49,520
Gauze.

9
00:00:58,840 --> 00:00:59,480
Increase suction.

10
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:49,840
Let's continue.

11
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:50,320
Okay.

12
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:52,600
Director Lin really is

13
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:53,560
pulling people back from death's door.

14
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,640
Hello, OR.

15
00:01:59,280 --> 00:01:59,880
This is Liu Guili.

16
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:00,720
Director Lin,

17
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:01,480
are you out of surgery?

18
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,640
No. What's wrong?

19
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:03,840
The ER admitted

20
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,920
a 23-week pregnant woman.

21
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:06,240
She just had a cardiac MRI.

22
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,320
They want us and Cardiology

23
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,200
to do a hybrid procedure.

24
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,320
What does that have to do with me?

25
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:11,640
Something urgent came up here.

26
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,600
I can only ask you to help.

27
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,440
Thanks. Thank you.

28
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,400
I've sent the patient

29
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,240
to the hybrid OR.

30
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,200
I'll send her details

31
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,080
to your phone right away.

32
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,200
Milk tea's on me later.

33
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:19,880
I... I...

34
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,120
Director Lin.

35
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,800
You've had plenty of milk tea this month.

36
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,400
This is your second cup today.

37
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:48,840
Director Lin.

38
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:50,960
Where's Cardiology?

39
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,280
They're outside getting family consent.

40
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:53,840
They'll be here soon.

41
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,320
Where's the chart?

42
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:56,480
Over there.

43
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,240
When is Cardiology coming?

44
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,320
Are we doing this surgery or not?

45
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,800
If they don't come soon, I'll...

46
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,800
Why is it you?

47
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:29,840
You'll what?

48
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:32,840
I'll...

49
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,120
Wait a little longer.

50
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,200
I just wanted to tell you in person.

51
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,200
I'll be leaving for a while.

52
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:00,800
To Guizhou.

53
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:04,960
To clear your head?

54
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,320
I've already spoken with President Cui.

55
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,160
Medical aid to Guizhou.

56
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:11,960
Yes.

57
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,200
I heard this year

58
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,040
no one has signed up yet.

59
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:16,520
I want to give it a try.

60
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,720
This is too sudden, Xiaofeng.

61
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,240
Have you thought it through?

62
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,400
In our local area,

63
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,760
there are many children

64
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:25,760
like Caiyun.

65
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,440
Right now, our local hospital

66
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,440
depends entirely on us old doctors.

67
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:31,720
Or else it's

68
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,960
fresh graduates.

69
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,560
There's a serious gap in between.

70
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,280
There's no way around it.

71
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,880
The conditions are poor.

72
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:39,040
Doctors in their prime

73
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:39,920
are hard to keep.

74
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,240
You said

75
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:43,760
whatever choice we make,

76
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:45,600
we must respect science

77
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,200
and put patients first.

78
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,400
I've always remembered that.

79
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:53,760
So,

80
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,120
whether it's treating patients

81
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,960
or helping the local hospital

82
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:59,320
train new doctors,

83
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,080
I want to do something.

84
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:03,960
I'm sure.

85
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,040
Right now,

86
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,640
it's what I most want to do.

87
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:14,960
Looks like our strike team

88
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:16,800
will have to stay in its sheath

89
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,480
for a while.

90
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,760
Let's call it

91
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,480
sharpening our blades separately.

92
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,320
When you come back,

93
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:23,640
two blades together.

94
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,560
Who could stand against us?

95
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,600
Look. We're in Dongjiang.

96
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:41,640
Look outside.

97
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:42,760
What is that?

98
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,160
The sea.

99
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,840
Isn't it beautiful?

100
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,400
I want to go play there.

101
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,760
You can after the surgery.

102
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,120
Then you can even go swimming.

103
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,200
Look over there.

104
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,040
I'm hot.

105
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:12,600
I don't feel well.

106
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,200
I'll get you some water.

107
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:21,320
Xuemei.

108
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:22,920
Are you feeling unwell?

109
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,600
Xuemei. Xuemei.

110
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,160
Talk to me, Xuemei.

111
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:28,200
Xuemei.

112
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:28,760
What's wrong?

113
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:29,200
Xuemei.

114
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:30,960
Xuemei.

115
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:31,520
Prepare oxygen.

116
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:32,480
Come on, step aside.

117
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:41,080
Oxygen saturation is low.

118
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:42,480
How much longer?

119
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,440
Thirty minutes.

120
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:44,240
Lao Liu.

121
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:45,080
Notify Dongli Hospital.

122
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,080
Have the ER ready.

123
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:46,840
Okay.

124
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,080
Xuemei, relax.

125
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:57,840
Master.

126
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:58,920
There are two more patients in the van.

127
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:00,160
Settle them, then come find me.

128
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:00,480
Got it.

129
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,200
Hurry, take her. Quick.

130
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:02,440
Come on.

131
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:03,480
Easy, easy. Careful.

132
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,200
Easy, easy.

133
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:06,960
Director Kong.

134
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:08,520
Pregnant woman with atrial septal defect,

135
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,320
3.2 centimeters.

136
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:10,520
Twin pregnancy.

137
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,480
Since mid-pregnancy,

138
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,440
she's shown signs of cardiac dysfunction.

139
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,040
Moderate pulmonary hypertension.

140
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,040
Sudden acute heart failure.

141
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:15,600
Okay.

142
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:16,800
Make way ahead.

143
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:19,800
Careful.

144
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,520
Xuemei's atrial septal defect

145
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,400
means

146
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,320
there's a hole

147
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:23,920
in the wall inside her heart.

148
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,600
The standard approach

149
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:27,720
is interventional closure under X-ray by Cardiology.

150
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:28,800
But considering

151
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:29,640
Xuemei is pregnant,

152
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:30,600
we cannot ignore

153
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,400
the harm from radiation.

154
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:32,320
But if we use

155
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,440
traditional surgery

156
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,440
to suture the defect,

157
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,600
it must be done with

158
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,440
cardiopulmonary bypass support.

159
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,600
Director Lin.

160
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:40,840
Where's Cardiology?

161
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,720
Based on

162
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,640
the current test results,

163
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:44,320
I plan to perform

164
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:46,080
a hybrid surgery combining internal and surgical approaches.

165
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,320
I... I agree.

166
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,760
I agree.

167
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:49,600
Sign here.

168
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,320
The patient's cardiac MRI

169
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,120
measured pulmonary blood flow

170
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:02,560
against systemic blood flow.

171
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:03,320
The ratio is 2.2.

172
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:04,480
This suggests pulmonary hypertension

173
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:05,520
is caused by the ASD shunt.

174
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:06,840
And her ASD is quite large,

175
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,400
near the IVC with a short rim.

176
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:09,520
I've read the chart.

177
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:10,600
Same as before.

178
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:12,200
I start, then you take over.

179
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,240
Blades out.

180
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:37,800
I plan to perform

181
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,440
a hybrid surgery combining internal and surgical approaches.

182
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,040
A surgeon will

183
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:42,520
make a small incision below her ribs

184
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,200
to partially expose the heart.

185
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:47,880
Then I'll take over

186
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,240
and puncture the heart surface,

187
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:50,240
delivering the occluder

188
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,440
directly to the ASD,

189
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:52,200
closing the hole.

190
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,400
The entire procedure

191
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,640
is ultrasound-guided,

192
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:55,720
with no radiation harm,

193
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:57,280
and avoids the risks

194
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:58,200
from cardiopulmonary bypass.

195
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,200
How's it going?

196
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:04,240
Liu Dong.

197
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:04,960
Xiao Zhu.

198
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:06,040
Come here.

199
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,040
Guess who this is.

200
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,400
Who?

201
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:09,880
Doesn't he look familiar?

202
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:10,520
Who?

203
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:12,120
Look closely.

204
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:15,440
Director Zhou.

205
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,200
Director Zhou is back!

206
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:19,520
What an unexpected surprise.

207
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:53,960
Have I been

208
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,600
doing too many night shifts lately?

209
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:55,520
Am I hallucinating?

210
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,400
What hallucination?

211
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:58,800
That's Director Lin.

212
00:10:59,520 --> 00:11:00,800
Our top cardiac surgeon.

213
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:01,720
Why is he

214
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,720
assisting someone else?

215
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,120
This kid only came last year.

216
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,440
He doesn't know Director Zhou.

217
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:09,520
Director Zhou.

218
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:10,720
My mentor.

219
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:11,960
Just returned from Guizhou aid work.

220
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:12,760
Watch and learn.

221
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:17,040
This

222
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:19,560
is the legendary dream team,

223
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,480
the Cardiac Center strike team.

224
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,960
With ultrasound guidance,

225
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,240
you can only see the heart clearly.

226
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,400
You can't see the guidewire path.

227
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:32,640
It's like at night,

228
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:33,520
holding a lantern

229
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:34,280
while backing into a parking spot.

230
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:35,280
So,

231
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:37,320
we make a small incision below the ribs

232
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,800
to shorten the backing-up distance.

233
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:40,960
Even so,

234
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:43,040
it's still difficult.

235
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,520
As expected of Director Zhou.

236
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:45,760
He's upgraded again.

237
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:49,080
Occluder in position.

238
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:57,720
Fixation is good.

239
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:01,840
Prepare to release.

240
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:05,920
Beautiful.

241
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:07,560
You scared me.

242
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,600
The strike team is reunited.

243
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,520
Are you that excited?

244
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:12,200
I've been waiting forever, okay?

245
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,040
Release complete.

246
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,200
The patient you brought back.

247
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:31,320
May she live a long life.

248
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:45,760
Don't worry.

249
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:46,840
The surgery went well.

250
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,240
All of Xuemei's indicators

251
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:48,920
are stable.

252
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,280
The babies' fetal heart rates are stable too.

253
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,080
For the next 24 hours,

254
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,440
she needs to stay in the ICU.

255
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:54,480
If there are no problems,

256
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,560
she can move to a regular ward.

257
00:12:56,160 --> 00:12:56,800
If you want to wait for her,

258
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:57,840
you can wait outside the ICU.

259
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,120
Thank you, Director Zhou.

260
00:12:59,200 --> 00:12:59,840
Thank you, doctor.

261
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:01,840
Over... over there.

262
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:02,240
Yes.

263
00:13:02,520 --> 00:13:03,280
Just go straight over.

264
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,560
Okay, thank you.

265
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:11,320
Stop.

266
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:15,560
Why did you come back early

267
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:16,200
without telling us?

268
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:17,480
Trying to ambush us?

269
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:19,520
I wanted to surprise you.

270
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,560
You jerk.

271
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:22,920
You scared me to death.

272
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:25,280
Are you leaving again this time?

273
00:13:25,920 --> 00:13:26,400
No.

274
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,240
Welcome back.

275
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:29,920
I'm back.

276
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,240
Partner.

277
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:38,960
Without you, I hardly did

278
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,040
any hybrid procedures.

279
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:41,080
Still okay?

280
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:41,840
No decline.

281
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:42,840
Absolutely perfect.

282
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,160
Does Xiaoran know you're back?

283
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,840
How did she react when she saw you?

284
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,760
Brother!

285
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,520
Large ASD closure

286
00:13:56,560 --> 00:13:57,160
hybrid surgery

287
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:58,120
completed in one hour.

288
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:58,880
The surgery went well.

289
00:13:59,400 --> 00:14:00,920
But the patient is carrying twins.

290
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,160
Twins consume more oxygen.

291
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:03,760
Be sure to monitor closely

292
00:14:03,800 --> 00:14:04,720
oxygenation and blood pressure.

293
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,960
If MAP drops below 70,

294
00:14:07,040 --> 00:14:08,080
or oxygenation below 90,

295
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:09,080
report immediately.

296
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:10,200
Okay, got it.

297
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:15,760
The Cardiac Center ICU

298
00:14:15,800 --> 00:14:17,200
and the general ICU

299
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,200
focus on different things.

300
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:18,880
If our body

301
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:20,640
were a carriage,

302
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,800
then the heart

303
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:22,760
would be the horse that powers it.

304
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:24,440
Since Director Wang Xu

305
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:26,400
was transferred to the branch hospital,

306
00:14:26,400 --> 00:14:27,320
the general ICU,

307
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,760
inside and out,

308
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:29,320
has been handled by Xiaoran

309
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:30,320
on her own.

310
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,080
Lower-level hospitals also

311
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:32,880
send people here from time to time

312
00:14:32,920 --> 00:14:33,840
for specialized training in perioperative monitoring.

313
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:36,120
Dr. Fang.

314
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,160
One more question.

315
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:45,520
In a case like this,

316
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:46,840
Xiaoran has grown up.

317
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:47,600
What else do we need

318
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:48,880
to pay special attention to?

319
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:49,640
She is already

320
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:50,800
She's already

321
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,480
a mature cardiac intensivist.

322
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:54,880
Let's go.

323
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:57,440
Well? Hard to recognize, right?

324
00:14:57,560 --> 00:14:58,280
The general ICU

325
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,920
and the OR moved to the new building.

326
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,480
It feels changed,

327
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:04,520
and yet like nothing changed.

328
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:06,960
Just like your life and mine.

329
00:15:07,520 --> 00:15:08,040
Brother.

330
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:12,760
But some things

331
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:13,840
will never change.

332
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:15,200
As long as you know that.

333
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,320
Ignore me. Carry on.

334
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:18,320
Why did you come back early?

335
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:19,240
Does Mom know?

336
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,840
Surprise.

337
00:15:21,880 --> 00:15:23,120
No idea who he learned that from.

338
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,120
Surprise.

339
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:25,200
Then come to our place

340
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:25,760
for dinner after work.

341
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:26,760
Mom happens to be

342
00:15:26,760 --> 00:15:27,640
back from a trip tonight.

343
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:28,760
We haven't

344
00:15:28,760 --> 00:15:29,760
eaten together in so long.

345
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:30,320
Okay.

346
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:32,640
I probably can't.

347
00:15:33,280 --> 00:15:34,280
An emergency surgery just came in.

348
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,200
No idea when I'll finish.

349
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:36,480
All right.

350
00:15:36,760 --> 00:15:37,480
We'll save you food.

351
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:38,640
Don't worry about me. You eat.

352
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:44,200
Why have you lost so much weight?

353
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:44,920
Have I?

354
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:46,520
I think I'm okay.

355
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:47,840
You have.

356
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,880
You're thinner than at New Year.

357
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:51,800
Xiaorui is home too.

358
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:52,880
I'll ask him to order for me.

359
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:53,600
Tonight,

360
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:54,760
we'll just have a simple seafood hot pot.

361
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,720
Seafood hot pot is simple?

362
00:15:57,160 --> 00:15:57,760
Don't bother.

363
00:15:57,920 --> 00:15:58,760
Let's eat out.

364
00:15:58,920 --> 00:15:59,640
No.

365
00:15:59,800 --> 00:16:00,560
A family dinner is rare.

366
00:16:00,640 --> 00:16:01,480
Of course we should eat at home.

367
00:16:01,920 --> 00:16:03,040
And after we moved,

368
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:03,880
you've never been there.

369
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:15,200
This is the one we took at New Year.

370
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:16,480
Yes.

371
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:18,440
Xiaorui made it for me.

372
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:21,520
I read

373
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:22,160
Xiaorui's follow-up reports.

374
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,040
The disease is progressing slowly.

375
00:16:24,560 --> 00:16:25,520
It's fairly optimistic.

376
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:26,560
Yes.

377
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,520
But Lin Yi is still nervous.

378
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,600
He keeps opposing Xiaorui living on campus.

379
00:16:32,920 --> 00:16:33,640
He'd love to

380
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:34,840
keep the kid tied to him every day.

381
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:36,760
But I actually know

382
00:16:37,640 --> 00:16:38,840
Xiaorui doesn't want to keep

383
00:16:38,880 --> 00:16:40,200
being treated like a patient.

384
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:43,760
Has Lin Yi

385
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:46,200
been a little anxious lately?

386
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:48,960
His replies in the group chat

387
00:16:49,040 --> 00:16:49,760
are getting shorter.

388
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:50,760
And he doesn't send

389
00:16:50,800 --> 00:16:51,880
those funny things anymore.

390
00:16:54,520 --> 00:16:55,560
He's especially busy now.

391
00:16:55,920 --> 00:16:57,480
Aside from the hospital,

392
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:58,840
since last year,

393
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:00,200
he's been leading teams to other hospitals

394
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:01,640
to observe heart transplant surgeries.

395
00:17:02,560 --> 00:17:03,440
I'm also training in

396
00:17:03,520 --> 00:17:05,120
perioperative transplant nursing.

397
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,720
It's preparation for Xiaorui.

398
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:12,840
You've had it hard.

399
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:15,520
It's okay.

400
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:18,800
It's just sometimes

401
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:20,160
I do worry about Lin Yi.

402
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,600
After Brother Lin Hai passed away,

403
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,800
Xiaorui became his only family.

404
00:17:26,520 --> 00:17:27,200
Moving was also partly

405
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,440
because of that.

406
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:30,320
That old place

407
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,480
held too many memories for them.

408
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:34,960
I suggested moving out

409
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:36,520
to give him a new environment.

410
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:38,400
People have to look forward.

411
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:47,080
This way.

412
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:57,200
Er Yi, Er Yi, lights on.

413
00:17:59,560 --> 00:18:00,480
Who came up with that name?

414
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:01,840
Xiaorui did.

415
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:04,800
Surprise!

416
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:05,560
Welcome, welcome!

417
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:06,440
Welcome home!

418
00:18:06,840 --> 00:18:07,840
Didn't you say you had surgery?

419
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:08,600
You liar.

420
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:09,440
He surprised me,

421
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,640
so I had to surprise him too.

422
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:12,280
No wonder you kept

423
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:13,520
asking where I was.

424
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:15,040
Welcome home, Brother Feng.

425
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:17,840
This is only step one of the surprise.

426
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:18,560
It hasn't even started yet.

427
00:18:18,800 --> 00:18:19,520
Show Brother Feng around.

428
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:20,120
Come on, follow me.

429
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:20,800
What?

430
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:21,520
All right, Brother Feng.

431
00:18:21,800 --> 00:18:22,840
I'll give you a proper tour.

432
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:24,840
That room.

433
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:25,920
That room is theirs.

434
00:18:28,320 --> 00:18:29,840
This room next door is mine.

435
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:34,320
I told Brother Yi

436
00:18:34,840 --> 00:18:35,560
they could just rent

437
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:36,440
