438
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:38,160
But Brother Yi insisted.

439
00:18:38,840 --> 00:18:40,080
He even rented one near school.

440
00:18:40,800 --> 00:18:42,080
School clubs keep me busy.

441
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:43,480
I barely have time to come home.

442
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:45,400
Mainly because

443
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:46,840
someone thinks I'm a third wheel.

444
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:51,520
What is that smell? It's so strong.

445
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:53,080
Don't ask. Just eat.

446
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:53,920
Brother, look over there.

447
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:55,880
The birthday gift you gave him.

448
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:56,800
He's kept it there

449
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:57,320
