450
00:18:57,520 --> 00:18:58,280
Why didn't you open it?

451
00:18:58,520 --> 00:18:59,480
We don't have a record player.

452
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:00,440
Why open the vinyl?

453
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:01,720
Fine.

454
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:03,040
Next year's birthday gift.

455
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:05,120
Brother Feng.

456
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:06,480
Look at these big cameras.

457
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:07,480
Over there.

458
00:19:07,840 --> 00:19:08,440
And over there.

459
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:10,240
Brother Yi installed them all for me.

460
00:19:10,600 --> 00:19:11,480
I strongly objected.

461
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:13,440
So he didn't put one in my bedroom.

462
00:19:14,640 --> 00:19:16,040
I think there still aren't enough.

463
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:16,880
Teenage years.

464
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:17,760
He needs close watching.

465
00:19:17,760 --> 00:19:18,480
It's dangerous.

466
00:19:20,560 --> 00:19:21,400
Family Day.

467
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:23,480
Xiaoran came up with it.

468
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:24,720
She said once a week,

469
00:19:24,800 --> 00:19:25,200
the family

470
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:25,840
gets together.

471
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:27,800
Now that Brother Feng is back,

472
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:28,880
join us next time.

473
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:32,320
Look, I made all these.

474
00:19:32,840 --> 00:19:34,200
I sell them online now.

475
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:35,200
They sell really well.

476
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:35,960
Beautiful.

477
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:37,760
Look here too.

478
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:47,440
You've turned this into a botanical garden.

479
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:48,920
If you like them, Brother Feng,

480
00:19:49,240 --> 00:19:50,080
I'll give you two pots later.

481
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:50,600
Okay.

482
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:51,720
Coming.

483
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:53,800
Mom.

484
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:55,040
Xiaoran, come in.

485
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:55,800
Brother.

486
00:19:56,320 --> 00:19:57,200
Mom's back.

487
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:03,800
Mom.

488
00:20:07,080 --> 00:20:07,640
Xiaofeng.

489
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:13,400
Let me take your bag, Aunt Fang.

490
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:15,400
You're finally back. I missed you so much.

491
00:20:15,800 --> 00:20:16,240
Xiao Lin.

492
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,800
Why are you standing there?

493
00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:22,560
Come in.

494
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,240
I brought everyone some gifts.

495
00:20:26,600 --> 00:20:26,920
Mom.

496
00:20:27,520 --> 00:20:27,840
Okay.

497
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:29,440
Xiaoran.

498
00:20:29,560 --> 00:20:30,520
Thank you, Brother.

499
00:20:30,760 --> 00:20:31,080
What about mine?

500
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:31,880
I have one.

501
00:20:32,320 --> 00:20:33,440
So pretty.

502
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,080
And me? Mine?

503
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:36,480
This is a silver ornament.

504
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,240
So many.

505
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:41,080
Fish mint?

506
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:42,520
Bought at the station.

507
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:43,760
Does it look good?

508
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:44,720
Xiaoran looks good wearing it.

509
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:45,480
Does it?

510
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:45,880
It does.

511
00:20:46,080 --> 00:20:48,280
At the temple,

512
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:50,160
I got one for each of you.

513
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:53,120
Thank you, Mom.

514
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:53,880
Thank you, Aunt Fang.

515
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:54,560
Thank you, Professor Fang.

516
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:56,200
You all work so hard.

517
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,080
May it keep you safe.

518
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:00,800
All right.

519
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:01,840
Everyone's here.

520
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:03,720
The show is about to start.

521
00:21:03,760 --> 00:21:04,240
Come on.

522
00:21:04,240 --> 00:21:04,760
Clean up.

523
00:21:04,800 --> 00:21:05,200
I'll help.

524
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:14,240
The show is on.

525
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:15,600
I'll get the rice.

526
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:16,440
First dish.

527
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:17,920
Prepared especially for you:

528
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:19,400
ginger duck.

529
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:25,640
Ginger duck?

530
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:27,440
You can tell, right?

531
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:34,640
Open that.

532
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:35,200
Here.

533
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:38,560
This...

534
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:39,520
This is...

535
00:21:40,520 --> 00:21:41,560
Peel off the shell and you can eat it.

536
00:21:42,760 --> 00:21:43,120
Close it.

537
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:44,520
Lin Yi.

538
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:46,280
What happened to this rice?

539
00:21:46,320 --> 00:21:47,600
The rice is rice, the water is water.

540
00:21:48,800 --> 00:21:49,760
It wasn't plugged in.

541
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:50,920
I...

542
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:53,520
What is this?

543
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,160
Maybe soup.

544
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:02,880
This really is a surprise.

545
00:22:06,840 --> 00:22:08,720
Everything needs a Plan B.

546
00:22:09,520 --> 00:22:10,240
Surprise.

547
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:13,400
It's been ages since I had instant noodles.

548
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:14,880
Thank you, Xiao Lin.

549
00:22:15,520 --> 00:22:16,120
These aren't ordinary

550
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:16,520
instant noodles.

551
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:18,120
We have Guizhou fish mint.

552
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:20,440
I'm so happy.

553
00:22:20,560 --> 00:22:21,560
It's been so long since

554
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:22,400
the whole family was together.

555
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:23,720
Come on.

556
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,040
Mom.

557
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:25,240
Thank you.

558
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:26,240
Cheers.

559
00:22:26,280 --> 00:22:27,720
Welcome home, Xiaofeng.

560
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:28,520
Cheers.

561
00:22:28,600 --> 00:22:31,520
Cheers, cheers!

562
00:22:40,320 --> 00:22:41,280
I think Brother Feng came back

563
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,200
a bit tanned.

564
00:22:42,800 --> 00:22:43,880
The altitude there is high.

565
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:45,760
The UV is very strong.

566
00:22:46,280 --> 00:22:47,920
Didn't you use the sunscreen

567
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:48,840
I sent you?

568
00:22:49,200 --> 00:22:49,760
I did.

569
00:22:49,840 --> 00:22:51,200
Sometimes I was too busy.

570
00:22:51,520 --> 00:22:52,840
These two years in Guizhou,

571
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,480
you've kept in touch with Aunt Fang a lot.

572
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:57,240
Those two call every day

573
00:22:57,280 --> 00:22:58,120
and video chat.

574
00:22:58,400 --> 00:22:59,640
Mom is already busy.

575
00:23:00,080 --> 00:23:01,080
Then once they get on the phone,

576
00:23:01,080 --> 00:23:01,760
they talk for ages.

577
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:02,880
She has no time for me.

578
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:04,200
I never received

579
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:05,200
any sunscreen.

580
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:05,960
Favoritism.

581
00:23:08,040 --> 00:23:08,880
No favoritism.

582
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:10,520
If anything, it favors you.

583
00:23:13,040 --> 00:23:13,520
Xiao Lin.

584
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:15,880
As soon as he came back, you two did

585
00:23:15,880 --> 00:23:16,840
a hybrid surgery?

586
00:23:17,280 --> 00:23:17,720
Yes.

587
00:23:17,760 --> 00:23:18,760
He gave me work the moment he got back.

588
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:20,280
Did it go smoothly?

589
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:21,120
It did.

590
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:22,040
Good.

591
00:23:22,760 --> 00:23:23,480
The patient was in the van

592
00:23:23,520 --> 00:23:24,440
when she suddenly had an acute attack.

593
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:25,560
I was worried then.

594
00:23:26,600 --> 00:23:27,600
Luckily he was there.

595
00:23:42,720 --> 00:23:43,200
Don't worry.

596
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:44,400
I've read the other two cases

597
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,120
you brought back too.

598
00:23:45,320 --> 00:23:46,200
