was still worthwhile.

895
00:35:41,200 --> 00:35:42,280
The donor was 51.

896
00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:43,480
The recipient was 35.

897
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:45,800
That's the biggest age gap

898
00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:46,560
in any transplant I've observed this past six months.

899
00:35:47,880 --> 00:35:48,400
When I watch these

900
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:49,560
perioperative videos,

901
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:50,640
I keep thinking

902
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:52,080
life can actually

903
00:35:52,120 --> 00:35:53,960
connect and continue this way.

904
00:35:56,080 --> 00:35:57,840
How much longer do you have to observe

905
00:35:58,160 --> 00:35:59,160
before you can operate yourself?

906
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:00,640
I want to, too.

907
00:36:01,080 --> 00:36:02,160
But I still have a long way to go.

908
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:19,880
Where did Xiaorui go?

909
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:22,880
He went back to the dorm today. Forgot?

910
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:26,240
I forgot.

911
00:36:27,560 --> 00:36:29,040
You're taking him to the market Saturday.

912
00:36:29,320 --> 00:36:29,960
You didn't forget that, right?

913
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:34,520
Saturday.

914
00:36:34,840 --> 00:36:35,840
I'll take him.

915
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:39,840
But I didn't forget Family Day.

916
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:40,480
I've already planned it.

917
00:36:41,040 --> 00:36:42,320
I saw him watching videos lately.

918
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:43,800
Fishing, wire-fishing...

919
00:36:46,480 --> 00:36:47,520
Lure fishing.

920
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:48,760
Whatever kind of fishing.

921
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:50,720
This week's Family Day theme

922
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:51,520
is fishing.

923
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:52,160
How about it?

924
00:36:52,880 --> 00:36:53,520
I'll tell him.

925
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:55,600
Right.

926
00:36:56,120 --> 00:36:57,840
What happened

927
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:58,240
with He Xuemei's pulmonary atresia?

928
00:36:59,080 --> 00:37:00,400
It was found by accident

929
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,440
during her follow-up today.

930
00:37:03,040 --> 00:37:03,600
What does she think?

931
00:37:05,040 --> 00:37:06,520
She's considering in-utero intervention.

932
00:37:09,160 --> 00:37:09,720
Why?

933
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:12,720
She already has twins.

934
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:13,240
Why take

935
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:13,880
such a huge risk?

936
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:15,560
I don't support it.

937
00:37:17,200 --> 00:37:18,200
Brother doesn't support it either.

938
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,160
Director Zhou.

939
00:37:25,480 --> 00:37:25,920
Xuemei.

940
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:27,880
What's wrong? It's so late.

941
00:37:30,040 --> 00:37:30,640
I'm sorry.

942
00:37:30,720 --> 00:37:31,520
Sorry to bother you so late.

943
00:37:32,200 --> 00:37:32,520
Sit.

944
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:34,440
Thank you.

945
00:37:45,240 --> 00:37:45,800
Director Zhou.

946
00:37:46,040 --> 00:37:47,720
That

947
00:37:48,080 --> 00:37:49,120
in-utero surgery you mentioned before...

948
00:37:49,480 --> 00:37:50,200
I want to do it.

949
00:37:56,520 --> 00:37:57,600
I understand how you feel.

950
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:00,880
But that surgery is too risky.

951
00:38:02,240 --> 00:38:03,520
I know there are risks.

952
00:38:03,840 --> 00:38:04,560
I know all of that.

953
00:38:06,400 --> 00:38:07,200
But

954
00:38:09,480 --> 00:38:11,640
I don't want to lose this baby.

955
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,040
I want to save him.

956
00:38:22,640 --> 00:38:23,120
Director Zhou.

957
00:38:23,560 --> 00:38:24,480
Do you remember this?

958
00:38:48,720 --> 00:38:49,280
Nini.

959
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,280
Mommy is back.

960
00:38:52,080 --> 00:38:52,920
I'm sorry.

961
00:38:53,960 --> 00:38:55,600
Mommy shouldn't have gone

962
00:38:55,640 --> 00:38:57,240
so far away and been delayed.

963
00:38:58,800 --> 00:38:59,600
Don't sleep anymore.

964
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:01,520
Say something to Mommy, okay?

965
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:04,520
Your fingers are so cold.

966
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:07,200
You're too cold.

967
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:09,520
Mommy will cover you up.

968
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:10,800
Nini.

969
00:39:12,280 --> 00:39:13,200
Mommy will hold you.

970
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:13,800
Hold you.

971
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:15,040
Then you won't be cold.

972
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,200
Nini.

973
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:17,120
Nini.

974
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:18,200
Nini.

975
00:39:18,720 --> 00:39:19,560
Wake up, please.

976
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:20,760
Say something to Mommy,

977
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:21,520
please?

978
00:39:22,240 --> 00:39:22,720
Nini.

979
00:39:26,560 --> 00:39:26,960
Nini.

980
00:39:29,200 --> 00:39:29,880
Nini.

981
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:32,120
Nini.

982
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:39,800
It was cut during the rescue.

983
00:39:58,960 --> 00:40:00,480
Nini.

984
00:40:05,080 --> 00:40:05,720
It's Nini's.

985
00:40:07,800 --> 00:40:08,760
Yes, Nini's.

986
00:40:10,200 --> 00:40:10,760
Back then,

987
00:40:11,320 --> 00:40:12,200
after you

988
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:13,160
cut off that chain,

989
00:40:13,440 --> 00:40:14,720
I went to the market

990
00:40:14,800 --> 00:40:15,560
and bought

991
00:40:15,840 --> 00:40:17,200
a longer cord,

992
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:19,200
a red cord. Then

993
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:22,200
I thought she could stay here,

994
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,200
closer to me.

995
00:40:25,240 --> 00:40:25,920
Every day,

996
00:40:26,600 --> 00:40:28,200
thump, thump, thump, thump...

997
00:40:28,240 --> 00:40:29,160
I felt like

998
00:40:29,200 --> 00:40:30,720
she had never left me.

999
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:33,920
Like she was always by my side.

1000
00:40:38,440 --> 00:40:39,800
Director Zhou, I know

1001
00:40:40,560 --> 00:40:41,560
you're doing this for my own good.

1002
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:42,760
But

1003
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:45,840
I'm a mother.

1004
00:40:46,520 --> 00:40:47,320
I keep feeling

1005
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,880
Nini has come back to me.

1006
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:54,080
Other people may not want her,

1007
00:40:54,080 --> 00:40:55,720
but I can't abandon her.

1008
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:57,200
I...

1009
00:40:58,160 --> 00:41:00,400
I'm begging you. Please

1010
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:02,760
save her, okay?

1011
00:41:48,320 --> 00:41:48,720
Mom.

1012
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:50,960
Do you have time tomorrow?

1013
00:41:56,240 --> 00:41:58,440
Twenty-three-week twins.

1014
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:03,240
You're an expert in fetal intervention.

1015
00:42:04,200 --> 00:42:05,200
Back then, Nurse Yu's

1016
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,520
fetal pulmonary atresia

1017
00:42:07,080 --> 00:42:07,920
was also overcome by you.

1018
00:42:08,960 --> 00:42:10,160
I wanted to ask for your opinion.

1019
00:42:12,120 --> 00:42:13,400
A twin pregnancy

1020
00:42:13,520 --> 00:42:15,080
is much more complicated

1021
00:42:15,080 --> 00:42:16,200
than Nurse Yu's case back then.

1022
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:18,520
The interventional risk will also be very high.

1023
00:42:20,720 --> 00:42:21,800
Considering the mother

1024
00:42:22,120 --> 00:42:23,480
and the other child,

1025
00:42:23,960 --> 00:42:25,160
I lean toward giving up.

1026
00:42:29,080 --> 00:42:30,200
So there really is no chance?

1027
00:42:32,200 --> 00:42:32,600
Xiaofeng.

1028
00:42:34,160 --> 00:42:35,920
This is a critical time

1029
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,080
in your application.

1030
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:38,520
The Guizhou congenital heart project

1031
00:42:38,560 --> 00:42:39,520
is a plus for you.

1032
00:42:40,560 --> 00:42:41,440
If something goes wrong

1033
00:42:42,120 --> 00:42:43,320
and there is a medical dispute,

1034
00:42:43,600 --> 00:42:44,720
it will be very unfavorable

1035
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:46,520
for your application.

1036
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:48,160
Do you understand that?

1037
00:42:50,200 --> 00:42:50,600
So,

1038
00:42:51,440 --> 00:42:52,520
you still want to try?

1039
00:42:53,560 --> 00:42:53,880
Yes.

1040
00:42:55,560 --> 00:42:56,520
Even if it affects me,

1041
00:42:57,840 --> 00:42:58,840
I still want to try.
